text: Oswaldo Enrique López Arellano (30 June 1921 – 16 May 2010) was a politician from Honduras. He was president of the country twice, first from 1963 to 1971 and then from 1972 to 1975. Arellano died on May 16, 2010 from prostate cancer. ==Other websites== *Obituary Category:1921 births Category:2010 deaths Category:North American politicians Category:Presidents of Honduras
